        {
            "id": "urn:summary_document_slides:quartr.com:3888009:0",
            "title": "Hyundai Rotem: Sales rose in Q2 2026, but profit margins and new orders declined year-over-year",
            "description": "<div class=\"body-Xl9a4Ubk body-nzzZVyQ3 content-nzzZVyQ3\"><div class=\"symbolsContainer-uFduEtAF logosContainer-diQOvrPB\" data-no-swipe=\"true\"></div><div><span><p class=\"\"><span>Q2 2026 delivered strong sales growth and improved cash position, but operating profit and net income margins declined year-over-year. New orders dropped sharply, and segment performance was mixed, with AD &amp; RH leading growth while Eco Plant contracted.</span></p><p class=\"\"><span>Original document: </span><a class=\"link-zw5jRdec\" href=\"https://www.tradingview.com/accounts/signin?next=https%3A%2F%2Fnews-mediator.tradingview.com%2Fdoc-screener%2Fv1%2Ffiles%2Furn%3Aslides%3Aquartr.com%3A3888009-17a94c8c952540bc858ee566920d49e2\" target=\"_blank\">Hyundai Rotem Co. [064350] Slides Release — Jul. 24 2026</a></p><section class=\"variant-secondary-Gmpzg_mv disclaimer-PlF2Sa64\"><b class=\"heading-wrapper-Gmpzg_mv\"><span class=\"heading-Gmpzg_mv\">Disclaimer</span></b><div class=\"content-Gmpzg_mv link-with-underline-Gmpzg_mv\"><span>This is an AI-generated summary and may contain inaccuracies. Please verify any important information with the original source.</span></div></section></span></div></div>",
            "link": "https://www.tradingview.com/news/urn:summary_document_slides:quartr.com:3888009:0-hyundai-rotem-sales-rose-in-q2-2026-but-profit-margins-and-new-orders-declined-year-over-year/",
